sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant E as Executor
    participant C as Controller
    participant A as Agent
    participant D as Docker daemon

    E->>C: Deploy (atomic step)
    Note over C: resolve image digest<br/>build ContainerSpec
    C->>A: EnsureContainerRunning
    A->>D: docker pull
    D-->>A: image ready
    A->>D: docker run -d
    D-->>A: container_id
    A->>D: start log tail
    D-->>A: stdout chunks
    A->>C: LogChunk
    D-->>A: health event
    A->>C: EventPush (healthy)
    A->>C: CommandResponse: ok
    C->>E: materialize outputs
